## FRONTEND

### Guidelines for REACT

#### PRIMEREACT

- Use PrimeReact components as the default UI building blocks instead of custom HTML when possible
- Prefer PrimeReact layout and form components (e.g., `Card`, `Button`, `InputText`, `DataTable`) for consistent styling
- Keep custom components thin wrappers around PrimeReact to avoid duplicating behavior
- When extending, follow PrimeReact theming and pass-through props rather than overriding styles directly
